PYRAMID BRUNCH TOTE!

This pattern prints a small triangle using repeated stitches.

INSTRUCTIONS:

Row 1: * ch 42 pic * repeat 5, ch 10 pic
Row 2: * ch 42 pic * repeat 4, ch 10 pic
Row 3: * ch 42 pic * repeat 3, ch 10 pic
Row 4: * ch 42 pic * repeat 2, ch 10 pic
Row 5: * ch 42 pic * repeat 1, ch 10 pic
